(7, 'Nefarious Activity and  Abuse ', 'Targeted attacks ', 'Attacks designed for a specific target, launched over a long period of time, and carried out in multiple stages. The main objective is to remain hidden and to obtain as much sensitive data/information or control as possible. While the impact of this threat is medium, detecting them is usually very difficult and takes a long time.  ', 'Infrastructure', NULL),
