(10, 'Nefarious Activity and  Abuse ', 'DDoS ', 'Multiple systems attack a single target in order to saturate it and make it crash. This can be done by making many connections, flooding a communication channel or replaying the same communications over and over. ', 'IoT devices', NULL),
