('2.4.10.5', 'The web user interface is protected by an automatic session idle logout timeout function.', 'M', 1, 'System', 'Software', '2.4.10', '4.1-1'),
('2.4.10.6', 'User passwords are not stored in plain text Strong passwords are required, and a random salt value is incorporated with the password. For further info see the 3GPP TS33.117 Password policy [ref 17], NIST SP800-63b [ref 26] and NCSC [ref 48].', 'M', 1, 'System', 'Software', '2.4.10', '4.1-1'),
('2.4.10.7', 'Where passwords are entered on a user', 'M', 1, 'System', 'Software', '2.4.10', '4.1-1'),
('2.4.10.8', 'The web user interface shall follow good practice guidelines, such as those listed in the OWASP [Ref 30].', 'M', 1, 'Business', 'Policy', '2.4.10', '4.1-1'),
('2.4.10.9', 'A vulnerability assessment has been performed before deployment and on an ongoing basis afterwards.', 'M', 1, 'Business', 'Process', '2.4.10', '4.1-1'),
