('2.4.4.8', 'The hardware incorporates physical protection against reverse engineering. The level of protection must be determined by the risk assessment.', 'M', 2, 'System', 'Hardware', '2.4.4', NULL),
('2.4.5.11', 'Development software versions have any debug functionality switched off if the software is operated on the product outside of the product vendor’s trusted environment.', 'M', 2, 'Business', 'Process', '2.4.5', NULL),
